    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理您的 Bodacious 1980 年代游戏商店</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/c45aaf9bf24ae162bfe26e628f7dc978.poster.avif?t=1765635887\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/c45aaf9bf24ae162bfe26e628f7dc978.webm?t=1765635887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买、库存和销售视频游戏、游戏机、海报和杂志以获取利润。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提高商店的声誉以获得必要的产品许可证。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过投资随着时间的推移发布的新小工具和系统，优化商店的生产力。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >订购、库存和销售管状产品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/2663c43ed07c54868efe67be5a19a6f8.poster.avif?t=1765635887\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/2663c43ed07c54868efe67be5a19a6f8.webm?t=1765635887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现 80 多种独特的视频游戏和游戏机出售给客户。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100% 委托手绘的艺术作品让您的产品设计感到自豪。每个占位符人工智能生成的产品艺术目前正在被替换！ </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参加视频游戏大会并收集名片，给供应商、商场租户和其他企业打电话。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赚一大堆硬币来升级</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/60b47a6b01b1017d8f105a71d8643c76.poster.avif?t=1765635887\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/60b47a6b01b1017d8f105a71d8643c76.webm?t=1765635887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当新单位可用时，立即认领它们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买货架、海报和演示摊位以影响客户参与度。  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断完善您单位的产品布局，以最大限度地提高您的利润率。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >留意你的库存</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/e70ae5e3e4d63b356dd105e83e5414ae.poster.avif?t=1765635887\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/e70ae5e3e4d63b356dd105e83e5414ae.webm?t=1765635887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在向您的库存中引入新产品时，请考虑类型、发布日期、控制台兼容性和其他元数据。       </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分析库存电子表格以了解产品的性能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据需要调整产品价格，以衡量不断变化的客户兴趣。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握你的时间，最大限度地利用你的时间<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/42875abc9fa1498bbf3134166e3c6bdb.poster.avif?t=1765635887\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090010/extras/42875abc9fa1498bbf3134166e3c6bdb.webm?t=1765635887\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用商场营业时间前后所提供的时间处理公司业务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主动订购热门产品，以最大限度地提高发布日销量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在圣诞节期间抓住机会赚大钱。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这只是创世记！你能活到90年代吗？</p>",
